  ('rgn_philistia', '블레셋 평원', '지중해 동안 평원의 블레셋 5도성: 가사·아스돗·아스글론·가드·에그론.', '📍', null, 31.6, 34.65, '[[31.2, 34.3], [31.3, 34.32], [31.45, 34.4], [31.55, 34.5], [31.65, 34.55], [31.78, 34.65], [31.85, 34.78], [31.85, 34.92], [31.85, 34.95], [31.65, 34.95], [31.45, 34.95], [31.3, 34.95], [31.2, 34.95], [31.2, 34.78], [31.2, 34.55], [31.2, 34.4]]'::jsonb, 'region', null, null, 80, '{"era_judges","era_monarchy","era_nt_apostolic"}'::text[], '{}'::text[]),
